                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d418">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Memorandum left at the Department of State by Baron von
                        Sternburg.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">German Embassy</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-08-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 23, 1900</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Chinese minister in Berlin has been informed that the German Government can
                    not enter into any negotiations with Li Hung Chang because it is not clear from
                    whom he has received his credentials and what credentials he holds as to
                    negotiations with the powers.</p>
            </div>
